Asset & Protocol Disclaimer:

This project is an independent, fan-made recreation of the Windows Live
Messenger 2009 experience. It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or
associated with Microsoft Corporation or the Crosstalk.im project.

- This client connects to Crosstalk.im community servers but is developed
  independently. It is not an official Crosstalk client and the Crosstalk
  team bears no responsibility for this project.
- Certain UI assets (icons, sprites and fonts) are derived from or inspired by
  Windows Live Messenger, which is the property of Microsoft Corporation.
- The MSNP protocol implementation is based on publicly documented protocol
  specifications and community research. It is not derived from decompiled
  or proprietary Microsoft source code.
- AI-generated assets are included and are not claimed as original
  Microsoft works.

